For the stable distribution (jessie), this problem has been fixed in version 2.5.39-8+deb8u1.

For the testing distribution (stretch), this problem has been fixed in version 2.6.1-1.

For the unstable distribution (sid), this problem has been fixed in version 2.6.1-1.

